---
title: Brown Sugar Chocolate Chip Mug Muffins with Orange Slices & Chocolate Ganache
description: 15-minute muffins from start to finish? We’ll get out of your way so you can get right to baking! For this chocolatey orange-infused breakfast treat, you’ll add chocolate chips, orange zest, brown sugar, and crème fraîche to our versatile batter mix, divide between mugs, and microwave for just about two minutes. Serve straight from the mug with orange slices and a creamy chocolate ganache (that’s frosting with a fancy name) for dipping or spreading. It’s a fast and friendly breakfast in a flash!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6509a4e550d57dbb4c05cefd-f19b743f.jpeg
